	HtURLCodec.
	(Deserialize): Decode it.

	* htmerge/htmerge.h: #include <HtURLCodec.h>
	* htmerge/htmerge.cc (main): Check HtURLCodec for errors.
	* htnotify/htnotify.cc (main): Ditto.
	* htsearch/htsearch.cc (main): Ditto.
